  <steps>
    <step num="0">Slice bread into cubes. </step>
    <step num="1">In a bowl, add egg, milk, cinnamon, and vanilla, and mix. </step>
    <step num="2">In a microwave-safe mug, place half of the cubed bread and desired amount of blueberries. </step>
    <step num="3">Place the rest of the bread, berries, and the egg mixture into the mug. </step>
    <step num="4">Microwave for 1½ minutes or until egg is fully cooked. </step>
    <step num="5">Drizzle maple syrup. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
